#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn4.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. Life Span "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn4.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Dutiyaāyusutta "
msgstr "10. Life Span (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn4.10:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "sn4.10:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the squirrels’ feeding ground. "

msgctxt "sn4.10:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā … pe … etadavoca: "
msgstr "There the Buddha … said: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn4.10:2.1"
msgid "“Appamidaṃ, bhikkhave, manussānaṃ āyu. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, the life span of humans is short. "

msgctxt "sn4.10:2.2"
msgid "Gamanīyo samparāyo, kattabbaṃ kusalaṃ, caritabbaṃ brahmacariyaṃ. "
msgstr "You must go to the next life. So you should do what is skillful, you should practice the spiritual life. "

msgctxt "sn4.10:2.3"
msgid "Natthi jātassa amaraṇaṃ. "
msgstr "No-one born is immortal. "

msgctxt "sn4.10:2.4"
msgid "Yo, bhikkhave, ciraṃ jīvati, so vassasataṃ appaṃ vā bhiyyo”ti. "
msgstr "A long life is a hundred years or a little more.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn4.10:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked went up to the Buddha and addressed him in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.109, sc4
msgctxt "sn4.10:4.1"
msgid "“Nāccayanti ahorattā, "
msgstr "“The days and nights don’t rush by, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:4.2"
msgid "Jīvitaṃ nūparujjhati; "
msgstr "and life isn’t cut short. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:4.3"
msgid "Āyu anupariyāyati maccānaṃ, "
msgstr "The life of mortals keeps rolling on, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:4.4"
msgid "Nemīva rathakubbaran”ti. "
msgstr "like a chariot’s rim around the hub.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.243, sc5
msgctxt "sn4.10:5.1"
msgid "“Accayanti ahorattā, "
msgstr "“The days and nights rush by, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:5.2"
msgid "jīvitaṃ uparujjhati; "
msgstr "and then life is cut short. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:5.3"
msgid "Āyu khīyati maccānaṃ, "
msgstr "The life of mortals wastes away, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:5.4"
msgid "kunnadīnaṃva odakan”ti. "
msgstr "like the water in tiny streams.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn4.10:6.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ bhagavā, jānāti maṃ sugato”ti dukkhī dummano tatthevantaradhāyīti. "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The Buddha knows me! The Holy One knows me!” miserable and sad, vanished right there. "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn4.10:6.2"
msgid "Paṭhamo vaggo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn4.10:7.1"
msgid "Tapokammañca nāgo ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:7.2"
msgid "subhaṃ pāsena te duve; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:7.3"
msgid "Sappo supati nandanaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:7.4"
msgid "āyunā apare duveti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
